title: Does God Exist Series Package - 24 Lectures
description:
Does God Exist?

Can men and women living in the 21st century really believe in God?
These video lectures are part of a series designed to demonstrate that science and faith are friends and not enemies.
Your presenter is a public high school science teacher, not a minister.
He was an atheist for many years, but came to believe in God through his studies in science.
